* 1 large onion, finely chopped (about 1 cup)
* 2 cloves of garlic, minced (about 2 tablespoons)
* 1/2 cup of vegetable oil (or sunflower oil)
* 2 tablespoons of white wine vinegar (or apple cider vinegar)
* Salt and black pepper to taste (about 1 teaspoon each)
* Fresh parsley, chopped (about 1/4 cup)
